    <p>
        Rob is Fluent in both his native English and German and has a good working knowledge of both
        Spanish and Arabic. Rob has been in the education sector for the last 15 years. He started out
        in US state schools, then moved overseas to start his context based learning for engineering,
        which he jointly developed with John Murphy. He specialises in technical English, and has
        developed bespoke English curriculum and courses for refrigeration, mechanical engineering
        as well as soft skills. He has lived and worked in Asia, Europe and the Middle East, along
        with his native United States. His greatest professional enjoyment is to collaborate with
        those who have life experience and help to translate that into marketable jobs skills.
    </p>
</div>

